{"tid":327702,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"豬蛇入一入嚟，唔該！","createTime":"2017-07-19T03:41:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T05:19:39.000Z","uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"42f891b07d7f3e1eb047c3362978bc58a044e6af","tid":327702,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T03:41:48.000Z","msg":"死返入垃圾桶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/113839_6f410b082ac929813094c49cde5f1459.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F113839_6f410b082ac929813094c49cde5f1459.jpg&h=daad1186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大基奧特沒想到的是 會來中國坐進垃圾桶思考人生<br />\n<br />\n　　熱！熱！熱！<br />\n<br />\n　　這是阿仙奴球星們來到中國上海後最深刻的印象，上海又悶又汗的「濕熱」，讓來自英倫島國的大牌們有點吃不消，紛紛鑽進「垃圾桶」里避暑。<br />\n<br />\n　　在阿仙奴的訓練場旁，這個特設的裝備可派上了大用場，雖然「出身不好」是個垃圾桶，但此刻儼然已化身為人見人愛的高級冰療器，裡面不光裝滿了水，還加入了冰塊，難怪阿仙奴的球員們一看到這個「垃圾桶」，就迫不及待的要鑽進去。<br />\n<br />\n　　韋碧克興奮的跳了進去，艾倫尼在裡面樂得合不攏嘴，藍斯嫌不過癮還讓隊友往頭上繼續倒冰塊，禾確特則在桶中露出享受的表情&hellip;&hellip;是啊，這麼熱的天，能在冰水裡泡泡，就是很好的事情了，誰還會去管這個桶原來是干什麼用的？<br />\n<br />\n　　大基奧特則又留下了經典造型，他站在垃圾桶里，目光深邃的望向遠方，手輕輕撫摸著鬍鬚，似乎在思考著什麼。此次中國行之前，基奧特很興奮的說：「我以前去過日本、越南，但還沒去過中國，我喜歡體驗新的經歷和探險，我已經迫不及待想到中國去看一看了&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n　　說這話的時候，基奧特可能不會料到，到了中國，自己會坐在一個垃圾桶里思考人生&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n　　（legion）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/114050_ca1f67e6140d479345a6b98cb1fe855e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F114050_ca1f67e6140d479345a6b98cb1fe855e.jpg&h=fc6f15ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/114122_30dc8f508c2b13f8408b9beb5bb80332.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F114122_30dc8f508c2b13f8408b9beb5bb80332.jpg&h=7d6f6207&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/19/114123_30dc8f508c2b13f8408b9beb5bb80332.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F19%2F114123_30dc8f508c2b13f8408b9beb5bb80332.jpg&h=9578f2a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6a9486d898e6060a5e58568ad87885af16043b8","tid":327702,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T03:44:32.000Z","msg":"牙狗又比人玩"},{"pid":"0dac236fc6c557dfa2cb5daf4cac32491d03af77","tid":327702,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T03:46:20.000Z","msg":"出街睇路"},{"pid":"fe5f52c369bdb4aa4c7c24a4c8db69c766f70950","tid":327702,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T03:55:45.000Z","msg":"其實幾型"},{"pid":"c46cc5208e7a47380493de2aff0057e20ae549ee","tid":327702,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T04:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去返晒應該去既地方"},{"pid":"2d7ac4331b19158c06e310220675b3db1bf057a2","tid":327702,"uid":1289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T04:02:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"991aaf3cf68f3477f5951c3e59901ebedf006688","tid":327702,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T04:48:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去返晒應該去既地方</blockquote><br />\n希望你都去"},{"pid":"f0ff57a7d8122674ea067e4bc8746e2f4e3bf439","tid":327702,"uid":14965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T04:57:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去返晒應該去既地方</blockquote><br />\n希望你都去</blockquote><br />\n曼迷去既地方只會係天堂"},{"pid":"9dc901a10e7a4a32fc69f054b2dcefeaf0739db7","tid":327702,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T05:19:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去返晒應該去既地方</blockquote><br />\n希望你都去</blockquote><br />\n曼迷去既地方只會係天堂</blockquote><br />\n方包皮純"}]}